<main>
  
  <section class="section">
    <div class="has-text-centered">
      Choose from either <%= link_to "Chemical" , subtype_survey_path(subtype: "chemical") %> , <%= link_to "Physical" , subtype_survey_path(subtype: "physical") %>
          or  <%= link_to "Biological" , subtype_survey_path(subtype: "biological") %> to start entering data.
    </div>
  </section>
  <div class="container">
  <div class="columns is-centered">
    <div class="column is-two-thirds">

      <section class="panel choose-panel ">
        <div class="panel-heading choose-panelhead">
          <%= link_to (image_tag "measure.jpg", class: "choose-image" ), subtype_survey_path(subtype: "physical")%>
        </div>
        <div class="mr-2 ml-2 pb-2">           
          <span class="title is-5">
            <%= link_to "Physical" , subtype_survey_path(subtype: "physical") %>
          </span>
          <p>Choose this for collecting data about the physical characteristics of the river and its surroundings. <br />
            e.g. Width, depth, man made structures, the flow regime, and examinations of the river bank .</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="panel choose-panel">
        <div class="panel-heading choose-panelhead">
          <%= link_to (image_tag "kit2.jpg" , class: "choose-image" ), subtype_survey_path(subtype: "chemical")%>
        </div>
        <div class="mr-2 ml-2 pb-2">           
          <span class="title is-5">
            <%= link_to "Chemical" ,  subtype_survey_path(subtype: "chemical")%>
          </span>
          <p> Choose this for collecting data about the chemical characteristics of the river, with a focus on the water. pH (Acidity), Nitrogen (nitrates), Phosphorus (phosphates), Conductivity, Temperature <br />
        </div>
      </section>


      <section class="panel choose-panel">
        <div class="panel-heading choose-panelhead">
          <%= link_to (image_tag "stream.jpeg" , class: "choose-image" ),  subtype_survey_path(subtype: "biological") %>
          
        </div>
        <div class="mr-2 ml-2 pb-2">           
          <span class="title is-5">
            <%= link_to "Biological" ,  subtype_survey_path(subtype: "biological")  %>
          
          </span>
          <p>Choose this for contributing observations about the biological characteristics of the river.  <br />
            Describe the riparian vegetation growing on the river banks<br />
            Observations about macroinvertebrats and the living things on the river bed such as algae, moss, leaf litter, submerged plants, dead wood or animals and non livings such as boulders, stones, gravel or clay.</p>
        </div>
      </section>




    </div>
  </div>
</div>

</main>


<div id="modal-onboard" class="modal" data-controller="tips">
  <div class="modal-background"></div>
  <div class="modal-content">
  
    <div class="box">
      <h4 class=" title is-6">Getting Started</h4>
      <div id="tips-container" class="">
        <div class="block">
          <div id="tip-0" class="tip tip-0 is-hidden">
            <p> <span class="icon is-small"><i class="fas fa-clipboard-check"></i></span> Choose physical, biological or chemical. </p>
            <p> <span class="icon is-small"><i class="fas fa-clipboard-check"></i></span> Some questions require a kit or special equipment.</p>
            <p> <span class="icon is-small"><i class="fas fa-clipboard-check"></i></span> Turn on Location on your phone before</p>
          </div>
          <div id="tip-1" class="tip tip-1 is-hidden">
            <p> <span class="icon is-small"><i class="fas fa-clipboard-check"></i></span> Any data is better than no data. It's okay if you don't answer everything. </p>
            <p> <span class="icon is-small"><i class="fas fa-clipboard-check"></i></span> Aim to survey an area of the river (transect) of about 20 meters</p>
          </div>
          <div id="tip-2" class="tip tip-2 is-hidden">
            <p> <span class="icon is-small"><i class="fas fa-clipboard-check"></i></span> Make sure you have a mobile phone or a way to call for help, and details of the nearest medical facility and how to get there.</p>
          </div>
          <div id="tip-3" class="tip tip-3 is-hidden">
            <p> <span class="icon is-small"><i class="fas fa-clipboard-check"></i></span> Wear sensible waterproof footwear with good grip. Wear appropriate clothing and protection for the environment and the weather</p>
            <p> <span class="icon is-small"><i class="fas fa-clipboard-check"></i></span> Know the weather forecast so that you know if there a chance of flooding or dangerous conditions. </p>
          </div>


        </div>
        <div class="level is-mobile">
          <div class="level-left">
            <a  data-action="tips#nextTip" class="button">&nbsp; Next Tip &nbsp;</a>
          </div>
          <div class="level-right">
            <button class="button closemodalbutton is-primary"  data-action="tips#hideTipsTemp"  >Got it</button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="block">
          <a  data-action="tips#hideTips"  class="">Don't show tips in future </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  
  </div>
  
  <button class="modal-close is-large" aria-label="close"></button>
  </div>
